title: Where in your RAM is "python san_diego.py"?
description:
Gumshoes, the rogue program ``san_diego.py`` is threatening to cause
havok! What is it doing to hide itself? What kind of things is it doing?
Who might it be communicating with? RAM is a big place - how can we even
find it, much less any of this information? Stay tuned and find out!
